I'll show you. Janet.

68
00:02:59,012 --> 00:03:00,388
-Hi, there.
-Hey, there.

69
00:03:00,471 --> 00:03:03,766
-Who the fork is that?
-Derek Hostetler, PI.

70
00:03:03,850 --> 00:03:06,519
Derek is my rebound guy.
I made him.

71
00:03:06,603 --> 00:03:07,645
Oh.

72
00:03:08,855 --> 00:03:10,648
