73
00:03:10,732 --> 00:03:12,650
-Yes. Because of what you said.
-Janet--

74
00:03:12,734 --> 00:03:14,193
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

75
00:03:14,277 --> 00:03:16,112
You know, you seem so sad.

76
00:03:16,195 --> 00:03:18,197
Do you want me
to make you a boyfriend?

77
00:03:18,281 --> 00:03:19,741
