-His brain is wrong.
-[laughs]

87
00:03:41,471 --> 00:03:43,056
-Mmm.
-Mmm.

88
00:03:43,139 --> 00:03:46,309
The goal is to tap the ball hard enough
to go through the wicket,

89
00:03:46,392 --> 00:03:48,394
